headline: Starbucks Donelson Expansion Tests Store Growth Against Rich Valuation Concerns
summary: Starbucks (NasdaqGS:SBUX) has been named lead tenant in a new multi-tenant retail development in Donelson, Tennessee. The project positions Starbucks as an anchor brand in a growing submarket near Nashville. The move comes as the company is working through pressures on same store sales and profitability. Starbucks, best known for its global coffeehouse network and branded consumer products, is still adding physical locations even as it deals with same store sales and margin pressures...
